These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, sprite
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, pomegranate, onion
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, mystery, action
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, turkish, australian
3 different pets are kept: pony, snake, mouse
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, boat, quad-bike
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the spanish##1
5. the turkish is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person eating cranberry is between the owner of the pony and the person eating pomegranate##2
8. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate      | mirinda      |
| Food          | pomegranate   | cranberry   | onion       |
| Movie-Genre   | action | comedy | mystery    |
| Nationality   | australian  | spanish    | turkish    |
| Pet           | snake    | mouse    | pony |
| Transport     | boat  | quad-bike     | motorbike        |

