.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, water
There 3 different types of food: lime, strawberry, pineapple
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, martial-arts, adventure
There are 3 different nationalities: british, french, colombian
3 different pets are kept: mouse, turtle, bird
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, water-polo, parkour
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person eating lime##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the french##1
6. the person eating pineapple is between the colombian and the person drinking water##2
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | coffee     | iced-tea        | water      |
| Food          | strawberry    | pineapple       | lime  |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | martial-arts | mystery    |
| Nationality   | colombian | british   | french    |
| Pet           | turtle      | mouse  | bird      |
| Sport         | parkour    | water-polo      | badminton |

