.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, lettuce, cabbage
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, skydiving, baking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, electronic, funk
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, argentine, indonesian
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, hedgehog
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, motorbike, bike
1. the person who's hobby is baking is between the indonesian and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
2. the argentine is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the japanese is the japanese##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is the fan of electronic##1
5. the argentine is on the left of the fan of country##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person eating blueberry##2
7. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
8. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
9. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | blueberry  | lettuce    | cabbage   |
| Hobby         | fishing | baking | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | funk       | electronic    | country |
| Nationality   | indonesian    | argentine  | japanese  |
| Pet           | bird     | hedgehog   | guinea-pig       |
| Transport     | motorbike | scooter     | bike       |

