2. the owner of the lizard is the person eating pomegranate##1
3. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1
4. the chinese is on the far right##1
5. the fan of metal is the owner of the ferret##1
6. the designer is between the person eating lemon and the owner of the rat##2
7. the argentine is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
8. the scientist is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |      2       |       3       |
| Food          | eggplant           | pomegranate       | lemon       |
| Job           | journalist | designer    | scientist |
| Movie-Genre   | romance      | time-travel | comedy        |
