The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, jazz, ambient
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, soccer, snowboarding
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, skateboard, roller
1. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person watching thriller movies and the fan of ambient##2
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person watching western movies is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person eating lemon##2
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |       3       |
| Food          | avocado      | banana  | lemon         |
| Hobby         | hiking   | camping    | rock-climbing       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | western | scientific          |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | jazz         | ambient         |
| Sport         | cricket | soccer     | snowboarding |
| Transport     | skateboard      | roller        | ship          |

