The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, action, mystery
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, gospel, soul
3 different pets are kept: dog, cat, chinchilla
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, snowboarding, badminton
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, snowmobile, ship
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the quad-bike and the owner of the chinchilla##2
3. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the fan of blues##1
8. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

